# ✅ Updated **gradle.properties** (project-level)

This is the **critical fix**. Add/replace with:

```properties
# --- Disable any download ---
org.gradle.java.installations.auto-download=false

# --- Disable detection (prevents Gradle from ignoring your JDK) ---
org.gradle.java.installations.auto-detect=false

# --- Explicit JDK path ---
org.gradle.java.installations.paths=/usr/lib/jvm/java-21-openjdk-21.0.10.0.7-1.el9.x86_64

# --- 🔥 MOST IMPORTANT: force Gradle to use this JVM ---
org.gradle.java.home=/usr/lib/jvm/java-21-openjdk-21.0.10.0.7-1.el9.x86_64

# --- CI stability ---
org.gradle.daemon=false
org.gradle.jvmargs=-Xmx2g -Dfile.encoding=UTF-8
```

